{
  "stem": "7506.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And [PAUSES] soon they-- and they-- they had a lot of food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They gave food, [PAUSES] the army ration food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And Luba took charge of all that, to dole out what she must've thought was right for us and what was not right for us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then-- I spoke a few words of English, not many.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES] I remember people came into the barrack where we were.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "A British cameraman came in the barrack, took films and/or photographs in the barrack.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Took a photograph of my sister, [PAUSES] amongst others.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And [PAUSES] being-- I was 13 years old then, because I'm born March.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I was liberated a month after my birthday.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I was not bar mitzvahed, because there was no bar mitzvah in the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I spoke-- I went up to a few of the soldiers and asked if they knew my uncles, because my uncles were in England.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I thought by that time my uncles must've been in the military.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I was 13 year old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, do you know my Uncle Sam Rabbie?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Do you know Michael Rabbie?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Do you know them?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, I had no idea what a vast apparatus an army is, you know at that time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were then-- after we were liberated, a few days afterwards, we were taken to a place-- all the children-- in the camp still, and we were told to take all our clothes off.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We took all the clothes off, and they had, like, insect sprays, and they sprayed us with white powder, which I then knew was DDT.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were sprayed all over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like, we came, like-- like zombies, all white with the DDT.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My sister was still able to walk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We never saw our clothes again.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
